{{Infobox Figure Skating Competition | title= 1980 Prague Skate | image= | imagesize= | caption= | comptype= | startdate= 7 November | enddate= 9 November 1980 | skatingseason= | location= [[Prague]], [[Czechoslovakia]] | host= | venue= | prizemoney= | championmen= {{flagathlete|[[Jozef Sabovčík]]|TCH}} | championladies= {{flagathlete|[[Carola Paul]]|GDR}} | championpairs= {{flagathlete|[[Birgit Lorenz]] / [[Knut Schubert]]|GDR}} | championdance= {{flagathlete| [[Elena Garanina]] / [[Igor Zavozin]]|URS}} | previouscomp= [[1979 Prague Skate]] | nextcomp= [[1981 Prague Skate]] | previousgp= | nextgp= }}
The '''1980 [[Prague Skate]]''' was held November 1980. Medals were awarded in the disciplines of [[single skating|men's singles, ladies' singles]], [[pair skating]], and [[ice dancing]].
