'''AGF Håndbold''' is a [[team handball|handball]] club from [[Aarhus]], [[Denmark]]. Currently, AGF Håndbold competes in the women's [[Danish 1st Division (Handball)|Danish 1st Division]]. The home arena of the club is [[Atletion]].
