'''Adama Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Adama]], [[Ethiopia]]. It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home stadium of [[Adama City]]. The stadium has a capacity of 4,000 people.
