The '''Kushiro Ice Arena''' (釧路アイスアリーナ) is an arena in the city of [[Kushiro]], [[Hokkaidō]], [[Japan]]. It is primarily used for [[ice hockey]], and is the home arena of [[Nippon Paper Cranes]] of the [[Asia League Ice Hockey]].
It was opened in 1996 and holds 2,539 seats, plus near 500 standing-room only.
It is situated in the [[Japan National Route 38]] close to the home of the Cranes, the Nippon Paper Kushiro plant.
