'''Thijs Visser''' (born October 19, 1989) is an [[Aruba]]n [[sailing|sailor]]. He competed at the [[2016 Summer Olympics]] in the [[Sailing at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Nacra 17|Nacra 17]] race with [[Nicole van der Velden]]; the two placed 16th.<ref>{{cite web|title=Thijs Visser |url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/athlete/thijs-visser |website=Rio 2016 |accessdate=August 20, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820174529/https://www.rio2016.com/en/athlete/thijs-visser |archivedate=August 20, 2016 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Nacra 17 Mixed - Standings |url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/sailing-standings-sa-nacra-17-mixed |website=Rio 2016 |accessdate=August 20, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820173614/https://www.rio2016.com/en/sailing-standings-sa-nacra-17-mixed |archivedate=August 20, 2016 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>

