{{Infobox football biography | name = Vladimir Forbs | image = | fullname = Vladimir Soares Forbs | height = {{height|meters=1.75|precision=0}} | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1992|4|14|df=y}}<ref>[http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs..vladimir.153648.en.html Vladimir] 22.03.2014, footballdatabase.eu</ref> | birth_place = [[Guinea-Bissau]] | currentclub = [[S.C. Praiense|Praiense]] | clubnumber = 6 | position = [[Midfielder (association football)|Midfielder]] | youthyears1 = 2009–2011 | youthclubs1 = [[C.S. Marítimo|Marítimo]] | years1 = 2011–2012 | clubs1 = [[C.S. Marítimo B|Marítimo B]] | caps1 = 0 | goals1 = 0 | years2 = 2013 | clubs2 = Oeiras | caps2 = 4 | goals2 = 0 | years3 = 2013 | clubs3 = [[FC Osaka]] | caps3 = 7 | goals3 = 3 | years4 = 2014 | clubs4 = [[FC Nitra]] | caps4 = 7 | goals4 = 0 | years5 = 2014–2015 | clubs5 = [[F.C. Tirsense|Tirsense]] | caps5 = 15 | goals5 = 2 | years6 = 2015–2016 | clubs6 = [[Atlético Clube de Portugal|Atlético CP]] | caps6 = 8 | goals6 = 4 | years7 = 2016– | clubs7 = [[S.C. Praiense|Praiense]] | caps7 = 12 | goals7 = 1 | club-update = 2 April 2017 | nationalteam-update = }}
'''Vladimir Soares Forbs''' (born 14 April 1992) is a [[Guinea-Bissau|Bissau-Guinean]] [[association football|football]] midfielder who currently plays for [[S.C. Praiense|Praiense]].
